{"text_id":133583,"tokens":["To"," answer"," your"," question"," of"," whether"," Leonardo"," Da"," Vinci","'","s"," research"," led"," to"," any"," technological"," advancement",","," the"," truthful"," answer"," is",":"," yes","."," Leonardo"," was"," far"," and"," beyond"," a"," man"," of"," his"," time"," and"," even"," sometimes"," ahead"," of"," it","."," During"," his"," life"," he"," made"," countless"," research"," of"," areas"," as"," diverse"," as"," anatomy",","," engineering",","," optics",","," astronomy"," and"," even"," mathematics",".","\n","One"," of"," his"," greatest"," legacies"," was"," his"," work"," on"," the"," principles"," of"," flight"," and"," mechanics","."," From"," these"," studies",","," he"," designed"," a"," number"," of"," concepts"," for"," machines"," and"," aircraft",","," including"," the"," helicopter",","," the"," hang"," glider"," and"," tank","."," These"," inventions"," weren","'","t"," created"," during"," his"," lifetime",","," but"," did"," form"," the"," basis"," of"," later"," designs"," and"," inventions",".","\n","Moreover",","," he"," made"," significant"," contributions"," towards"," the"," development"," of"," the"," clock","."," His"," sketch"," of"," an"," oscillating"," pendulum",","," for"," example",","," enabled"," Galileo"," to"," invent"," the"," pendulum"," clock"," and"," is"," the"," same"," combination"," of"," pendulum"," and"," escape","ment"," that"," is"," used"," in"," all"," grandfather"," clocks"," today","."," In"," addition"," to"," this",","," his"," studies"," on"," optics"," revolution","ised"," the"," study"," of"," lenses"," and"," thus"," gave"," rise"," to"," the"," invention"," of"," the"," telescope",".","\n","The"," modern"," day"," parachute"," is"," also"," thought"," to"," be"," based"," on"," a"," design"," by"," Da"," Vinci","."," Da"," Vinci","'","s"," parachute"," design"," includes"," a"," pyramid","-","shaped"," parachute"," made"," out"," of"," linen","."," Although"," he"," never"," tested"," this"," design",","," one"," of"," his"," theories"," was"," that"," air"," resistance"," would"," slow"," the"," fall"," of"," a"," man"," in"," a"," parachute","."," This"," idea"," was"," first"," tested"," in"," France",","," a"," full"," ","2","4","0"," years"," after"," da"," Vinci"," wrote"," his"," thoughts"," on"," the"," concept",".","\n","Additionally",","," one"," of"," the"," most"," significant"," inventions"," of"," Da"," Vinci"," is"," the"," concept"," of"," the"," ball"," bearing","."," He"," demonstrated"," the"," idea"," in"," a"," sketch"," and"," concept"," for"," a"," ball"," bearing"," that"," eventually"," led"," to"," the"," invention"," of"," the"," roller"," bearing","."," The"," roller"," bearing"," allowed"," for"," mechanical"," components"," to"," turn"," more"," smoothly"," and"," without"," friction",","," revolution","izing"," the"," entire"," history"," of"," machines",".","\n","In"," conclusion",","," it"," can"," be"," seen"," that"," Leonardo"," Da"," Vinci"," did"," not"," only"," make"," technological"," advancements"," during"," his"," lifetime"," -"," his"," research"," often"," provided"," the"," foundations"," for"," the"," technological"," advancements"," of"," later"," generations","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"davinci","label":1}